title: Easy Image Dataset Augmentation with TensorFlow - KDnuggets
excerpt: What can we do when we don't have a substantial amount of varied training data? This is a quick intro to using data augmentation in TensorFlow to perform in-memory image transformations during model training to help overcome this data impediment.
